    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 03 — CRM Deal Stage Automator\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Configure IMAP credentials with your sales inbox\n2. Replace HubSpot stage IDs (get them from HubSpot Settings > CRM > Deals > Pipelines)\n3. Add a step to look up deal_id by contact email before the Route node\n4. Replace all credential IDs\n\n**Note:** You'll need a HubSpot lookup node between 'Parse Classification' and 'Route by Intent' to find the deal_id from the sender's email address.",
        "height": 800,
        "width": 1684
      },
      "id": "94f1b995-1834-43fc-aecc-ef3aed8066ad",
      "name": "Setup Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
